{"article_id":"EtPSLJGahourCPyA","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump , in his first statements","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"since lawyer Rudy Giuliani revealed overnight","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that the president reimbursed attorney Michael Cohen for a hush-money payment to porn star Stormy Daniels ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"said","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"the money was meant to stop \" false \" allegations","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"and stressed","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"campaign funds played no role .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"The president put out a three-part tweet about the $ 130,000","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Cohen paid to Daniels ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"whose real name is Stephanie Clifford ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"to stay quiet in the weeks before the 2016 election about accusations of an affair .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"\" Mr . Cohen , an attorney , received a monthly retainer , not from the campaign and having nothing to do with the campaign ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"from which he entered into , through reimbursement , a private contract between two parties ,","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"known as a non-disclosure agreement , or NDA , \"","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"Trump tweeted early Thursday .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"\" These agreements are very common among celebrities and people of wealth .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"In this case it is in full force and effect","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"and will be used in Arbitration for damages against Ms. Clifford","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"( Daniels ) .","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"The agreement was used","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"to stop the false and extortionist accusations","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"made by her about an affair , \"","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"Trump added .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"Trump continued :","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"\" ...despite already having signed a detailed letter","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"admitting","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"that there was no affair .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Prior to its violation by Ms. Clifford and her attorney , this was a private agreement .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Money from the campaign , or campaign contributions , played no roll","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"[ sic ]","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"in this transaction . \"","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"The president was referring to a letter","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"written and signed by Daniels in January ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"stating \" with complete clarity \"","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"that allegations of an affair with Trump were \" absolutely false. \"","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"Daniels also wrote , at the time ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"that rumors","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"that she received \" hush money \" from Trump","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"were \" completely false . \"","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Trump , however , also said last month","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"that he didn ' t know about the $ 130,000 payment .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"But Giuliani revealed Wednesday night on Fox News ' `` Hannity ''","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"that Trump indeed made the reimbursement .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"Giuliani , though , clarified Thursday on \" Fox & Friends \"","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"that Trump \" didn ' t know the details of this","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"until we knew the details of this \" a couple weeks ago .","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"He has said","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"Trump thought","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"it was to cover unspecified `` expenses . ''","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"Giuliani stressed","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"that this was a personal payment","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"and disputed any suggestion","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"that it was an unreported campaign contribution .","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"\" [ Cohen ] was trying to help the family .","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"... I think","depth":15},{"id":55,"text":"he was just being a good lawyer , \"","depth":15},{"id":56,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"\" That money was not campaign money , \"","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"Giuliani also said on `` Hannity . ''","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"\" It ' s not campaign money .","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"No campaign finance violation . \"","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"Giuliani ,","depth":15},{"id":62,"text":"who recently joined Trump 's legal team ,","depth":15},{"id":63,"text":"added","depth":14},{"id":64,"text":"that the money was \" funneled \" through a \" law firm","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"and the president repaid it . \"","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"Whether that argument holds up remains to be seen .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"A candidate is allowed to contribute an unlimited amount to his or her campaign .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"However , contributions are supposed to be officially reported .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"If the payments were wholly personal ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"said Richard L. Hasen , an expert in election law at the University of California , Irvine ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"there would be no campaign finance violations .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"But Giuliani 's argument","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"that the payment was unrelated to the campaign","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"could well be challenged .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"If it 's considered a campaign-related expense ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"the onus may have been on the president or his campaign to report it as a loan .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"`` The greatest significance is that it implicates the president , directly , ''","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Hasen told the Associated Press .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Daniels ' attorney , Michael Avenatti , said on MSNBC ' s \" Morning Joe \" Thursday morning","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"if it ' s \" true \" that Trump reimbursed Cohen ,","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"it ' s a \" crime \" with \" serious consequences . \"","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"Cohen previously has said","depth":5},{"id":84,"text":"the money","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"he paid to Daniels","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"came out of his own pocket .","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"Both Trump 's and Giuliani 's statements now seem to contradict Cohen 's account .","depth":4},{"id":88,"text":"Cohen is currently under criminal investigation as part of a grand jury probe","depth":2},{"id":89,"text":"looking into his personal business dealings .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":179,"left":177,"right":178,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":96,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":93,"right":95,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":93,"left":92,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":92,"left":0,"right":91,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":95,"left":4,"right":94,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":94,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":176,"left":171,"right":175,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":155,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":99,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":7,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":97,"right":10,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":118,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":110,"right":117,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":110,"left":102,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":101,"right":14,"relation":"attr